{"tid":2421254,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"點解TXMIYAMA咁少人聽","createTime":"2021-02-24T11:22:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T16:41:58.000Z","uid":58740,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"27b66f31a076620bd4129b0b92bb8f41b6902013","tid":2421254,"uid":58740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:22:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dQ4R8fV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdQ4R8fV.jpg&h=e43af323&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTxmiyama，人稱「Jap-Boy」，是居港的加拿大籍日本人，正是香港常見的「third-culture kid」。Txmiyama 的歌詞英、日文夾雜，內容無畏無懼，一針見血，以獨特視角描繪出香港的真實風景。〈5am Minibus〉裏一句歌詞就出現在金鐘反送中示威：「7K for a house like a cell/and you really think we out here scared of jail」，可見 Txmiyama 的歌曲令不少人產生共鳴。<br />\n<br />\nFor The City<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yiTVBiUo4aU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DyiTVBiUo4aU&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8Cbpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=78a0c6fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yiTVBiUo4aU</a><br />\nHOLLYWOOD ROAD<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c-wfKaxBwkc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dc-wfKaxBwkc&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8Cbpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=8accd38f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c-wfKaxBwkc</a><br />\n8 FOR 8<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2-CzJSg2kes\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2-CzJSg2kes&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8Cbpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=5b189d29\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2-CzJSg2kes</a><br />\nRED HORSE<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oVbI-_1nQUg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DoVbI-_1nQUg&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8Cbpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=728628d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oVbI-_1